{"tid":1732592,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"滙豐取消反修例活動眾籌戶口","createTime":"2019-11-18T02:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T02:31:27.000Z","uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d88f66538ebdc3d5e6fb24a0803c7f1a59979a39","tid":1732592,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:24:07.000Z","msg":"【給予30日通知 本周到期】滙豐取消反修例活動眾籌戶口 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2qmwfke\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2qmwfke&d=Iox0GB6uY5Umm6P4cmuVh%2B6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=b095c9e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2qmwfke</a><br />\n<br />\n本港社會衝突持續5個多月，隨着局勢升溫，坊間愈來愈多自發支持反修例的眾籌活動及團體，消息人士透露滙豐有一個企業銀行客戶，因為協助涉及抗爭活動的大型眾籌基金接受捐款，被指戶口實際用途與當初開戶用途不符，上月遭滙豐要求結束戶口。消息又稱，滙豐有給予該企業客戶30日通知期，並於本周到期，如果該企業未能在另一銀行開戶，將對該企業客戶原本業務及資金往來造成影響。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐發言人表示，作為負責任的金融機構，滙豐有必要了解客戶的背景和需要，並保障金融體系的健全，因此一向會定期檢視客戶賬戶的狀況，如果發現交易活動與開戶時所陳述的用途不相符，或客戶的資料出現遺漏，該行會主動檢視有關該賬戶的活動，同時有可能終止該賬戶。<br />\n<br />\n立法會金融界議員陳振英提醒各企業及個人，不應隨便為其他團體收取眾籌資金或捐款，因為此舉違反銀行開戶合約。他解釋，個人銀行戶口不可用作眾籌，銀行亦會要求個人客戶表明開戶目的，例如出糧戶口可用作收取薪金，倘若有大量或異常資金往來，銀行亦會向客戶查詢。<br />\n<br />\n#信報 #反修例運動"},{"pid":"0b464e88ba15938bc873137c00230b74b6ec7b5a","tid":1732592,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NdgS8Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NdgS8Y.jpg&h=fb14efa1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n老豆搵仔呼籲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你仲返工？去理大啦！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不落單<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不譴責<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不退縮"},{"pid":"cb10b88ca90b4d547a2ce0d7c99cb7f537e894e5","tid":1732592,"uid":163753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:24:50.000Z","msg":"裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1bdbc82de1434066f961c194de71b725ad2075","tid":1732592,"uid":229127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb10b88ca90b4d547a2ce0d7c99cb7f537e894e5","tid":1732592,"uid":163753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:24:50.000Z","msg":"裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:30:12.000Z","msg":"唔夠人手仲去裝修 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508a119c697079b6816bde89e2290ed444d3779c","tid":1732592,"uid":56410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb10b88ca90b4d547a2ce0d7c99cb7f537e894e5","tid":1732592,"uid":163753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:24:50.000Z","msg":"裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:31:27.000Z","msg":"咪玩野, 睇清楚HKMA對銀行要求先講<br />\nAML最近搞得越黎越大"}]}